OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FAdam Williams first started working at
OL,7,Fthe steelworks in Port Talbot as a 16-
OL,8,Fyear-old apprentice right out of
OL,9,Fschool.
OL,11,F18 years later, he "never thought"
OL,12,Fhe'd be working his last ever shift
OL,13,Fthere as traditional steelmaking came
OL,14,Fto an end in Port Talbot.
OL,16,FAdam is one of almost 2000 people
OL,17,Fwhose jobs were set be cut following
OL,18,FTata Steel's decision to close both
OL,19,Fblast furnaces in Port Talbot.
