OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FAfter spending the entirety of his
OL,7,Fadult life working at the plant, Adam
OL,8,Fsaid steelmaking was all he'd ever
OL,9,Fknown.
OL,11,F"Leaving work on my final shift, I
OL,12,Fdidn't realise how emotional I was
OL,13,Fgoing to be leaving for the last
OL,14,Ftime," Adam told ITV Wales.
OL,16,FBut, ever since Tata made an
OL,17,Fannouncement in January that it
OL,18,Fplanned to axe thousands of jobs
OL,19,Facross its UK operations, Adam has
OL,20,Fbeen working hard to prepare for life
OL,21,Fafter steel.
