OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FAfter speaking to a friend who was
OL,7,Fdoing something similar, he began to
OL,8,Fresearch what it would take to set up
OL,9,Fhis own cleaning business.
OL,11,FHe taught himself what to do through
OL,12,FYouTube videos, and took out a loan to
OL,13,Fbuy a van and all the cleaning
OL,14,Fequipment he needed.
OL,16,FNow, after months of building up a
OL,17,Fclient base alongside his full-time
OL,18,Fjob, he's grateful that his business
OL,19,Fis thriving.
