OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,F"It's been gaining traction through
OL,7,Fword of mouth, or pity, but I'll take
OL,8,Fboth really," Adam laughed.
OL,10,F"It's in my own hands now, which is
OL,11,Fdaunting to think but there is
OL,12,Fopportunity there as well... it's like
OL,13,Fa new dawn.
OL,15,F"I'm looking forward to what the
OL,16,Ffuture holds."
