OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FAdam is one of around 2500 people
OL,7,Facross Tata Steel UK who will lose
OL,8,Ftheir jobs before Christmas this year,
OL,9,Fwith the majority of those affected
OL,10,Fbased at the Port Talbot site.
OL,12,FThat number doesn't take into account
OL,13,Fthe many more contractors and workers
OL,14,Fin the supply chain who are also set
OL,15,Fto be impacted.
OL,17,FFor Adam, he's optimistic that he can
OL,18,Fcontinue to make a living in the area
OL,19,Flong after traditional steelmaking
OL,20,Fends.
