OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FBut, for many workers, there is still
OL,7,Funcertainty about what life after
OL,8,Fsteel could look like.
OL,10,FTata says it plans to build an
OL,11,Felectric arc furnace on the site which
OL,12,Fwould make steel by melting scrap
OL,13,Frather than using raw materials.
OL,15,FThe company said it wanted to turn to
OL,16,Fgreener methods of steelmaking in a
OL,17,Fbid to reduce its UK CO2 emissions by
OL,18,Ffive million tonnes per year and
OL,19,Freduce the "overall UK country
OL,20,Femissions by about 1.5%".
