OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FThe arc furnace is expected to be
OL,7,Foperational within three years, with
OL,8,Fthe steel giant emphasising it would
OL,9,Fmark the largest investment in the UK
OL,10,Fsteel industry for decades.
OL,12,FBut some workers are still in limbo
OL,13,Fabout whether they would be part of
OL,14,Fthat transition, while others will
OL,15,Fsoon join an already-challenging job
OL,16,Fmarket along with thousands of others.
