OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FIn response a support centre has been
OL,7,Fset up in Aberavon Shopping Centre in
OL,8,FPort Talbot to support those
OL,9,Fsteelworkers affected by the closure
OL,10,Fof the blast furnaces.
OL,12,FCommunity Union, the organisation
OL,13,Fbehind the centre, said the closure
OL,14,Fwill have a "huge" knock-on impact on
OL,15,Fthe local economy and community.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
