OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FThe training and support on offer will
OL,7,Fbe geared towards helping individuals
OL,8,Fto further their careers and find new
OL,9,Fjob opportunities in Port Talbot and
OL,10,Fthe surrounding areas, according to
OL,11,FCommunity.
OL,13,FThe union said the centre involves an
OL,14,F"ambitious partnership" with the Welsh
OL,15,Fand UK Governments and local agencies,
OL,16,Fincluding Careers Wales, Neath Port
OL,17,FTalbot Employability, Acorn employment
OL,18,Fagency, UK Steel Enterprise and Google
OL,19,FDigital Garage.
