OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FA Tata Steel spokesperson said they
OL,7,Fwere "deeply conscious" of the impact
OL,8,Fof its restructuring programme on
OL,9,Femployees, contractor partners and the
OL,10,Fwider community.
OL,12,FThey continued: "As part of our #20
OL,13,Fmillion contribution to the Transition
OL,14,FBoard fund, we have committed to
OL,15,Fsupporting the cost of establishing,
OL,16,Frefurbishing, and running the Support
OL,17,FHub in Aberafan Shopping Centre to
OL,18,Fensure all those who need to access
OL,19,Fsupport can do so."
