OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FSecretary of State for Wales and chair
OL,7,Fof the Tata Transition Board, Jo
OL,8,FStevens, said the funding from the UK
OL,9,FGovernment via the board is "already
OL,10,Fmaking a difference."
OL,12,FShe said: "We know there is still a
OL,13,Fhuge amount of work to do, but we are
OL,14,Falready seeing people successfully
OL,15,Fplaced in new jobs as a direct result
OL,16,Fof the #13.5 million that we made
OL,17,Favailable."
