OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FWelsh Government's Economy Secretary
OL,7,FRebecca Evans added: "We would all
OL,8,Fprefer to be in a position where this
OL,9,FCommunity Support Centre wasn't
OL,10,Fnecessary.
OL,12,F"But, it's important that we work
OL,13,Ftogether as we look towards the future
OL,14,Fand ensure that the very best and
OL,15,Fwidest support possible is there for
OL,16,Fpeople bearing the brunt of Tata's
OL,17,Fdecisions."
