OL,3,CLife after steel: What's next for
OL,4,Csteelworkers losing their jobs?
OL,6,FWhile Adam remains optimistic about
OL,7,Fthe opportunities his business will
OL,8,Fbring, the prospect of a future
OL,9,Fwithout steel is daunting for many
OL,10,Fother current and former steelworkers
OL,11,Fwho don't have work lined up.
OL,13,FWhat everyone seems to agree on is
OL,14,Fthat there are likely to be some
OL,15,Fdifficult months ahead.
